      "body" : "I don't like these type of tidy-up changes; our bottleneck is review and testing, and this just adds to our review and testing overhead with almost no benefit.\r\n\r\nAnd personally, I prefer to see the explicit type for trivial types like this; the added indirection of a typedef isn't worth it for me.",
